{% extends "_main.jinja" %}

{% block title %} Welcome to Bedeve {% endblock %}

{% block main %}
    {# main picture #}
    <div class="picture img-fluid" style="background:url(../static/images/main.png) no-repeat; background-size: cover;">
        <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-12 col-centered">
            <br>
            <br>
            <br>
            <div class="maintxt jumbotron-fluid text-center">
                <h1> BE Developer</h1>
                <h3> Time to start coding </h3>
            </div>
            <br>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    {# 3 things #}
    </div>
        <div class="threethingsheader">
      <div class="col col-12">
        <h1> FIP RULE </h1>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="flip-card col-12 col-md-4">
        <div class="flip-card-inner">
          <div class="flip-card-front">
            <h4 class="card-title">FUN</h4>
          </div>
          <div class="flip-card-back">
            <p class="card-text">
              It must be fun for you, that's the basis. Whatever you enjoy, you'll be good at it.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flip-card col-12 col-md-4">
        <div class="flip-card-inner">
          <div class="flip-card-front">
            <h4 class="card-title">IMAGINATION</h4>
          </div>
          <div class="flip-card-back">
            <p class="card-text">
              Imagination is also important, if you are proposing something, you have to think about it in your head first.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flip-card col-12 col-md-4">
        <div class="flip-card-inner">
          <div class="flip-card-front">
            <h4 class="card-title">PERSISTENCE</h4>
          </div>
          <div class="flip-card-back">
            <p class="card-text">
              You have to be persistent, it often happens that something doesn't work. If you want to be successful, you have to be persistent.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

{% endblock %}


